the shipment's origin and destination are under way. Prosecutor 
Jose Vicente Gonzalez reported on the findings and the steps 
that will be taken. 
  [Begin recording] [First reporter] [Question indistinct] 
  [Gonzalez] Today, the Treasury Police director general 
reported that the Treasury Police chief detected weapons inside 
a safe arriving from Miami at the airport. I went there with 
members of the Investigations Institute of the Attorney 
General's Office. First, the shipment was verified. The 
captain of the (?post) was advised. The weapons will remain at 
the (Combes) warehouse, which is right next door. We are 
conducting preliminary investigations. 
