<H3> <TI>   Secretary, Former Officials Summoned </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PY0503134294 La Paz Radio Fides Network in Spanish 1100 GMT 
5 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> PY0503134294 </F>
<F P=104>  La Paz Radio Fides Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] In a seemingly all-out war waged by the national 
government, the Santa Cruz Special Antinarcotics Force has 
summoned Susana Seleme, a former secretary to the president of 
the Republic [Jaime Paz Zamora]; Rolando Arostegui, a former 
Santa Cruz mayor under the Patriotic Accord administration; 
Carlos Valverde, a former Interior Ministry intelligence 
department chief and a former assistant to [former Interior 
Minister] Guillermo Capobianco; Orlando Elmer Saucedo, the 
Interior Ministry seizures department chief during Capobianco's 
tenure; and other officials whose names we were unable to obtain. 

</TEXT>

