  [Excerpt] Representatives from the Ministries of 
Construction of Vietnam and Cuba have signed a cooperation 
agreement in Havana. The document establishes that Cuban and 
Vietnamese construction forces will work on infrastructure 
projects in Vietnam. The Vietnamese delegation is headed by 
Professor (Nguyen Manh Kin), vice minister of construction. 
